def EffectResponseFunction(PreTest, PostTest):
    if (PreTest == PostTest and PreTest == '' and PostTest == ''):
        return 'NullNull'
    # elif PreTest == PostTest != '':
    elif (PreTest == PostTest and PreTest != '' and PostTest != ''):
        return 'XX'
    # elif PreTest != PostTest == '':
    elif (PreTest != PostTest and PreTest != '' and PostTest == ''):
        return 'XNull'
    # elif '' == PreTest != PostTest:
    elif (PreTest != PostTest and PreTest == '' and PostTest != ''):
        return 'NullX'
    # elif '' != PreTest != PostTest != '':
    elif (PreTest != PostTest and PreTest != '' and PostTest != ''):
        return 'XY'
    else:
        return 'Unknown'
